item.title: Jungwon Choi, Ph.D.
item.description: Doctoral Dissertation High-frequency, high-power resonant converter with wide bandgap devices for wireless power transfer systems Presented in 2018 Manuscript availabe here. Summary As demand for electric vehicles (EVs) grows, wireless power transfer (WPT) technology becomes beneficial by removing the need for manual intervention to charge EV batteries. These high-power applications require power electronics systems that not only efficiently deliver sufficient power, but are also small enough to be embedded in the EV.
